金庸群侠传游戏的命令分为下列几类：

［玩家命令］

alias   bt      ce      desc    exit    finger  help
hp      id      nick    passwd  quit    save    inventory
score   set     suicide time    title   unset   uptime
version who     wimpy   wizlist

［探险命令］

ansuan  ask     beg     buy     chat    close   drop
emote   fight   follow  get     give    go      halt
hit     kill    look    nuoyi   open    put     remove
reply   say     semote  shout   sleep   steal   team
tell    touxi   tune    unwield vote    wear    whisper
wield

［武功命令］

abadon(fangqi)  apprentice(bai) check(dating)   enable(jifa)
enforce(jiali)  exercise(dazuo) exert(yun)      expell(kaichu)
learn(xue)      meditate(tuna)  perform(yong)   persuade(quan)
practice(lian)  prepare(bei)    recruit(shou)   skills(cha)
study(du)       teach(jiao)


［巫师命令］

请参照 help wizcmds

